creator: ashishb
descriptionHtml:
Collecting useful snips of information is hard while traveling.
- VoiceNotes allows you to record a voice note
- VoiceNotes transcribes the note
- VoiceNotes records the GPS location and time as well
- VoiceNotes enables you to go through all the voice notes later at a convenient time.
- VoiceNotes works offline, so, no data connection is required to use it

For those who keep thinking of new ideas, concepts, or jokes, VoiceNotes allow you to jot it down before you lose that ephemeral stream of thought. You can share the recording or the text message into other apps later.

Vocenotes is the fastest player in town.

Note: on Android 12 and later, Google's on-device transcription does not work. So, a new offline transcription model has been added. This new model is English-only.
